719031f-a.title: Manhattan: Bradhurst Avenue - 150th Street
719031f-a.text:
Colonial Park: Children playing in the middle section of
this narrow park that parallels Bradhurst Avenue. Buildinms
seen on the east side of same are north from W. 147th Street.
No. 2 is eastward from the slope and shows a roup playing
baseball in the area above the childrens playground. In this
instance the buildinns seen are between 150th (right)and 151st
Streets.
Aumst 29, 1935.
View 2: September 1, 1935.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
